edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.tasks

Class StatisticDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
      • edu.ucdavis.cstars.client.tasks.StatisticDefinition

  • public class StatisticDefinition
extends com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject
    Class added v2.6 The StatisticDefinition class defines the type of statistics, the field used to calculate the statistics and the resulting output field name. Used to specify an array of statistic definitions for a query's outStatistics property. Requires ArcGIS Server service version 10.1 or greater
    Author:
    Justin Merz
